Title: Los isleros
Actors: Tita Merello, Arturo García Buhr, Roberto Fugazot, Enrique Fava
Plot: Leandro and the Carancha are inhabitants of the islands of the Parana Delta and agree a pair. They are rough persons done to the hard fight for the life in these places. They have a son who takes to the house a girl; the presence of her provokes the jealousies of the Carancha and his attitude leads dramatists moments.
